text: Thérèse Leduc (born 25 January 1934) is a French alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vosges (department)
